@startuml l1_activity
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title **Level 1 — Activity Diagram (Single Agent Baseline)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E3F2FD|Generic Agent (qwen2.5:14b)|
:Receive client question;
:Analyze the business context;
:Research the market landscape;
:Evaluate financial implications;
:Identify potential risks;
:Synthesize all findings;
:Write consulting report\nwith recommendations;
:Include self-evaluation\nin the report;

|Client|
:Receive consulting report\n(with embedded self-evaluation);

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator (gemini-2.5-flash)|
:Score report on 6-criterion rubric;
:Produce evaluation scorecard;

|Client|
:Receive final report + scorecard;
stop

note right
  **Level 1 Characteristics:**
  * 1 agent, 1 model (qwen2.5:14b)
  * No role separation
  * No tool access
  * No structured output
  * Self-evaluation only
  * Evaluator runs separately
  ----
  **Baseline** for progressive
  complexity comparison
end note

@enduml
